Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:12.16,GameSign,,0,0,0,,打敗了魔王吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:25.86,GameSign,,0,0,0,,勇者還忍著便意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.05,GameSign,,0,0,0,,勇者肚子裡一陣清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.55,GameSign,,0,0,0,,然而逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.56,GameSign,,0,0,0,,新•阿拉比嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.64,0:24:30.85,GameSign,,0,0,0,,魔王吉利被封印後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.14,0:24:32.56,GameSign,,0,0,0,,兩周!!!!!!!!!
